# Python Port Plan — Step 02: The Tool Registry

## Goal

Port `week1_baseline/ruby/02_the_registry` to
`week1_baseline/python/02_the_registry`. This step adds a `Registry` class
(registers tools onto a `Context` and dispatches calls to them by name) and
an `UnknownToolError` exception, on top of the same `Config`/`Tasks::Base`/
`Tasks::Player`/`Tool`/`Message`/`Context` already ported in step 1. Same
behavior, same example output shape, same shared `.boukensha/` fixture
directory as the Ruby version.

